Brief description

Poster, 'For your kind cooperation, thank you!', part of Seibu Railway 'Manner Poster' series, offset printed on paper, created by Yokoyama Yumiko (art director) and Kadowaki Takahiro (illustrator) for Dentsu Inc. under commission from The Seibu Railway Co., Ltd, December 2018
